---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="..." id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="h-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Welllkom' to my <span class="text-primary"> whiteborrred</span> jungl'Cita !
    <span class="text-primary"> Once upon a time</span> my name was <span
      class="text-primary">Quéméré</span
    >, and I used to be a <span class="text-primary">post-modern</span>, wild at
    Art,
    <span class="text-primary"> undergrrround</span> comiXmaker.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="https://astro.new/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="anchor" class="h-8" />
      <span>Yam What Yam</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://docs.astro.build/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="cross" class="h-8" />
      <span>Nest In Pace, Quéméré</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
